title: War of the Roses: There are flies everywhere
description: Renee is suspicious that her boyfriend is cheating on her for quite possibly one of the most ridiculous reasons.... she tells us that she's started to notice flies all over their place and that her boyfriend must be brining them in from another girl's house.  What is the reason for the flies and is Renee acting a little nuts?
